Lustre must be mounted as /mnt/lustre before running setup step and tests.

1) set the purpose environment variable
export PURPOSE=TMP_FS_MGR

2) setup the test environment
./1-test_setup.sh

3) Run the tests

for brief output:
	./2-run-tests.sh -q
for full output:
	./2-run-tests.sh
to run only some tests:
    ./2-run_tests.sh 3,4
